Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驅同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊呀 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}給你倒杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吵醒你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我一直在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}還沒完全睡醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}從前有部電影裡說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}豆蔻年華的女孩子趴著睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就證明她墜入了愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我倒是覺得為人父母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就算不看這種地方也會馬上知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不會有事先知道結局的愛情片的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你已經知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不…沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是知道了會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這種戀愛會很無聊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不太懂透子說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過要是真能預知未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就可以享受兩次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}媽媽 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就算知道未來是痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也能事先做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}儘是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能享受兩次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}說不定很美妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}如果能做出好作品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就可以再體會一次那種感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}如果是戀愛的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}如果是戀愛的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一條蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}蟲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是什麼蟲子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我們家的女兒雖然是個乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但畢竟正值豆蔻年華呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}豆蔻？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 透子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是沖倉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}上次 到最後你也沒說有什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.61,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我再打給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}掛掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一下子就被掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是上次的那個女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我去沖咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你沒做什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}經歷兩回初吻這種 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}做不到 做不到 做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}心臟要炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沖倉同學 剛才不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不好意思 我是祐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}話說 今天的集會上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有些事情想跟你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}咦 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今後怎麼能一直保持這種心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}該怎麼去見她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早安 大懶蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}媽媽叫我們吃飯 你沒聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…我剛才在換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早餐要涼了 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天去風道之前 我有些事要辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其實我只請透子先來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你去了小幸家的事我已經聽她說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸可能對祐有興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是或許太害羞了不敢直接說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是請不要告訴雪哉和柳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 大家都知…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因為我想親口跟他們說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 嗯 也是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.78,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天也真熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我已經告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}了不起 小柳好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我挺喜歡透子你那感覺良好又少根筋的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.01,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}最近怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.50,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我討厭熱天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.28,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我就開門見山地說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒錯 這次的主角就是小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是想給她個驚喜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之前的煙火大會她不是沒去成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以我想辦一場小幸也能參加的煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你們不這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}贊成 真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}通過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雖然總覺得作為考生 我們最近活動太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不過也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我去跟小幸說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明明在這裡接就可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是沒辦法在這接的電話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}誰打來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是大衛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼 要是知道他的聯絡方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就把他也請來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是說讓透子邀請他？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 那我來邀請他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我來請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道他家在哪 大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以說為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我們剛才正在討論要不要邀請大衛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}順水推舟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是井美 沖倉同學的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你竟然知道我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沖倉家在這附近很有名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你有時間的話 我想去外面說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我真是個名副其實的大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 這裡是沖倉家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沖…驅同學在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驅出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}井美同學也是你的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 算吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其實我根本就不想叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那不叫我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}世上的事情可不能簡單地由主觀願望決定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我們要辦一場煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我來邀請你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雖然你不想叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是又有不得不叫我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒必要專程去興風作浪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}自你來了之後我們這就風波不斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼可能開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那不是我的主要目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}和你一樣 我不是想做才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.46,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你和透子的關係算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你沒注意到透子的心意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子什麼都沒跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而且我也沒必要和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}高山向你告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你不會是還沒有回覆她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這次還是別叫驅同學了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你臉怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}總之很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}難道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}難道 難道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是被小雪打的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是我說重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}高山似乎向他表明了自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是不是對小雪做了很過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}其實最近好多事情我都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大家一起湊錢買的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}線香煙火 我很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}太好了 買了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼說也是給小幸辦的煙火大會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}本來是驚喜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你的心意我已經感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}歡迎回…來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那傢伙不來煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}發生什麼事了 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}兩個男人爭搶透子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我到底算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不是讓你道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道不能這樣一直下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我爸爸也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.82,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}討厭 這裡全是我的CD嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.25,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嘛 我是你的粉絲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.45,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}讓我為你彈一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.44,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好呀 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我媽媽來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我今天先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你媽媽是那個鋼琴家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一來這裡我就能安靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你媽媽是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她呀 是個不會停在一個地方的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不知道是由於職業還是由於性格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是個活潑的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小時候 不管媽媽做什麼我都覺得是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}該說是戀母情結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也有這麼想的時候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我都打了兩次電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子要說的那件事 差不多該告訴我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}兩次都沒有說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸說要住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雖然小幸說是住院檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要我別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是我看到了她住院的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你很擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱歉 透子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有件不得不跟你說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是打了沖倉同學的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你見過他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}現在我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}到校園裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我們把話說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子是站在我這邊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快去阻止小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他們要見到的話一定會不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}突然打了你 我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是你真覺得對不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就和我來場比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}正好這裡有合適的場地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}跑步？ 你跟我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能讓你認真起來的就只有跑步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你贏了 我就不會再見透子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我贏了 透子就是我的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你還有高山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}故意輸給我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}反正你根本就沒想跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不知道你的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是你選擇的做法最差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}別去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 煙火大會要延期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是大衛同學沒有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要不我們先來一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳說的是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我沒準備跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不想跑的我是不可能贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}發展成兩個人相爭 我究竟是想怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}自己也不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這麼說好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}這種話什麼也說明不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}總之我也許是希望聽到透子說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}「我是站在驅那邊的」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子是怎麼看「未來的碎片」的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能…能享受兩次 和心理準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你真的很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}之所以命名它為「未來的碎片」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是因為我把它當成了自己缺少的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不完整的我變成穩定形態時需要的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是那些碎片只是些微小的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}或是人們的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不再有其他的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}見到透子之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我漸漸懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我真正想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是那些莫名其妙的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是更清楚 更具象的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我聽到的 全是你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我看到的 也全是驅同學的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…找到了嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我討厭大衛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}未來是無法改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我和驅同學算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我今天先回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那個 請不要這麼遜
